      <title>Colophon</title>
      <link>https://marcandregoyette.com/en/colophon/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jul 2020 22:19:44 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://marcandregoyette.com/en/colophon/</guid>
      <description><h2 id="constraints">Constraints</h2>
<p>I chose to adopt some constraints while building this web site.</p>
<p><strong>Static site</strong>: The web site will be static and generated with my own static site generator.</p>
<p><strong>JavaScript</strong>: Avoid as much as possible the use of JavaScript.</p>
<p><strong>Tracking</strong>: Do not add Google Analytics or other trackers.</p>
<h2 id="fonts">Fonts</h2>
<p>The text on this web site use <a href="https://github.com/huertatipografica/Alegreya">Alegreya</a>, an open source font created by <a href="https://www.huertatipografica.com/en">Huerta Tipográfica</a>.</p>
<p>Code blocks use a monospace font that varies depending on the fonts installed on the operating system.</p>
</description>
